     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>¶ To the reader.</head>
   <l>Some ther be that do defye</l>
   <l>All that is newe, and euer do crye</l>
   <l>The olde is better, awaye with y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> new</l>
   <l>Because it is false, and the olde is true:</l>
   <l>Let them this boke reade and beholde</l>
   <l>For it preferreth y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> learnyng most olde.</l>
</div>
